v/a - Other Oz Hordes - Aus / NZ Mix Tape

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on January 12, 2024 Description from Terminal Escape:
Ripped a real banger set from Sydney's HITMEN a while back (check Escape Is Terminal for that magic) and someone was nice enough to cram a few bonus cuts at the end so....here you go. HENCHMEN, MUSHROOM PLANET and a gloriously brooding number from MELTING SKYSCRAPERS - it's a short little mix, but damn it's a good one. Thank you...and you're welcome too. OTHER OZ/NZ HORDES
